Let $$n\in\Bbb R^{2,1}$$ with $$\langle n,n\rangle=1.$$ A //hyperbolic half-space// is the intersection of $$H^2$$ with the half-plane $$\{x\in\Bbb R^{2,1}\mid\langle n,x\rangle\ge 0\}.$$

